import { Navbar, Nav, Container } from 'react-bootstrap';
import { LinkContainer } from 'react-router-bootstrap';  // Ułatwia łączenie Nav.Link z react-router

function TopNavbar() {
    return (
        <Navbar bg="dark" variant="dark" expand="lg" sticky="top">
            <Container>
                <LinkContainer to="/">
                    <Navbar.Brand>PokeFusion</Navbar.Brand>
                </LinkContainer>

                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                    <Nav className="me-auto">
                        <LinkContainer to="/">
                            <Nav.Link>Home</Nav.Link>
                        </LinkContainer>
                        <LinkContainer to="/fuse">
                            <Nav.Link>Fuse</Nav.Link>
                        </LinkContainer>
                        <LinkContainer to="/myfusions">
                            <Nav.Link>My Fusions</Nav.Link>
                        </LinkContainer>
                        <LinkContainer to="/premium">
                            <Nav.Link>Premium</Nav.Link>
                        </LinkContainer>
                    </Nav>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Container>
        </Navbar>
    );
}

export default TopNavbar;
